{"type":"message","id":"ffb14667","parentId":"e3a37d37","timestamp":"2026-03-12T00:23:08.992Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"用户问的是一个简单的问题：workspace 文件是否可以存到其他盘（非 C 盘）。这是一个配置/路径问题，不需要我实际操作，只需回答是否可行。\n\n根据 OpenClaw 的架构，workspace 路径是可以配置的。用户当前 workspace 在 C:\\Users\\28964\\.openclaw\\workspace，他们想移到其他盘（比如 D 盘、E 盘等）。\n\n答案是可以的，但需要：\n1. 移动 workspace 文件夹到目标位置\n2. 更新 OpenClaw 配置指向新路径\n\n用户明确说\"只需回答，不需要操作\"，所以我应该简洁回答。","thinkingSignature":"reasoning_content"},{"type":"text","text":"可以。\n\nOpenClaw 的 workspace 路径是可配置的，你可以把它放在任何盘（D 盘、E 盘等）。需要：\n\n1. 把整个 workspace 文件夹移到目标位置\n2. 更新 OpenClaw 配置指向新路径\n\n想迁移的话告诉我，我可以帮你操作。"}],"api":"openai-completions","provider":"dashscope-coding","model":"qwen3.5-plus","usage":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":0,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"stop","timestamp":1773274984934}}
{"type":"message","id":"65ab3896","parentId":"ffb14667","timestamp":"2026-03-12T00:25:54.219Z","message":{"role":"user","content":[{"type":"text","text":"Sender (untrusted metadata):\n```json\n{\n  \"label\": \"openclaw-control-ui\",\n  \"id\": \"openclaw-control-ui\"\n}\n```\n\n[Thu 2026-03-12 08:25 GMT+8] 在这里创建的定时任务是否是根据心跳执行的，如果没有配置心跳，定时任务还会执行吗"}],"timestamp":1773275154212}}
{"type":"message","id":"e460f27f","parentId":"65ab3896","timestamp":"2026-03-12T00:26:01.785Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"用户问的是关于 OpenClaw 中定时任务（cron）和心跳（heartbeat）的关系。这是一个技术问题，我需要解释清楚两者的区别。\n\n根据我的知识和工具描述：\n1. Cron 任务是通过 `cron` 工具管理的独立调度系统\n2. 心跳（HEARTBEAT.md）是另一种周期性检查机制\n\n它们是两个不同的系统：\n- Cron 任务：通过 cron tool 添加，有独立的调度器，会按照设定的时间/间隔执行，不依赖心跳\n- 心跳：是主会话定期被唤醒检查 HEARTBEAT.md 中的任务\n\n所以即使用户没有配置心跳，cron 定时任务仍然会正常执行。它们互不依赖。\n\n我应该简洁清楚地回答这个问题。\n","thinkingSignature":"reasoning_content"},{"type":"text","text":"不是。\n\n**定时任务（cron）和心跳是两个独立的系统：**\n\n| 机制 | 执行方式 | 依赖心跳 |\n|------|----------|----------|\n| **Cron 定时任务** | 由 Gateway 调度器独立管理，按设定时间/间隔触发 | ❌ 不依赖 |\n| **心跳检查** | 主会话定期被唤醒，读取 HEARTBEAT.md 执行任务 | ✅ 需要心跳配置 |\n\n**结论：** 即使没有配置心跳，通过 `cron` 工具创建的定时任务仍会正常执行。两者互不影响。"}],"api":"openai-completions","provider":"dashscope-coding","model":"qwen3.5-plus","usage":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":0,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"stop","timestamp":1773275154217}}
{"type":"message","id":"b26e091d","parentId":"e460f27f","timestamp":"2026-03-12T00:26:32.638Z","message":{"role":"user","content":[{"type":"text","text":"Sender (untrusted metadata):\n```json\n{\n  \"label\": \"openclaw-control-ui\",\n  \"id\": \"openclaw-control-ui\"\n}\n```\n\n[Thu 2026-03-12 08:26 GMT+8] \"bindings\": [\n // {\n // \"agentId\": \"main\",\n // \"match\": {\n // \"channel\": \"whatsapp\",\n // \"accountId\": \"personal\"\n // }\n // }\n ]\n讲一下这个配置"}],"timestamp":1773275192632}}
{"type":"message","id":"ee48bddc","parentId":"b26e091d","timestamp":"2026-03-12T00:26:36.910Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"用户询问的是 OpenClaw 中关于 bindings 配置的内容，这是关于消息路由/绑定的配置。让我解释这个配置的作用。\n","thinkingSignature":"reasoning_content"},{"type":"text","text":"这是 **消息路由绑定配置**，用于控制哪个 agent 处理哪个渠道的消息。\n\n**配置结构：**\n\n```json\n\"bindings\": [\n  {\n    \"agentId\": \"main\",      // 指定哪个 agent 处理\n    \"match\": {\n      \"channel\": \"whatsapp\",  // 匹配渠道\n      \"accountId\": \"personal\" // 匹配具体账号\n    }\n  }\n]\n```\n\n**作用：**\n\n- 当 WhatsApp (personal 账号) 收到消息时，路由给 `main` agent 处理\n- 注释掉 = 不启用这个绑定规则\n\n**使用场景：**\n\n如果你有多个 agent 或多个账号，可以用 bindings 精细控制消息路由：\n\n```json\n\"bindings\": [\n  {\n    \"agentId\": \"main\",\n    \"match\": { \"channel\": \"whatsapp\", \"accountId\": \"personal\" }\n  },\n  {\n    \"agentId\": \"support-bot\",\n    \"match\": { \"channel\": \"telegram\", \"accountId\": \"public-bot\" }\n  }\n]\n```\n\n**默认行为：** 没有 bindings 配置时，消息按默认规则路由（通常是 main agent 处理所有）。"}],"api":"openai-completions","provider":"dashscope-coding","model":"qwen3.5-plus","usage":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":0,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"stop","timestamp":1773275192637}}
{"type":"message","id":"9bef7d9a","parentId":"ee48bddc","timestamp":"2026-03-12T00:29:35.873Z","message":{"role":"user","content":[{"type":"text","text":"Sender (untrusted metadata):\n```json\n{\n  \"label\": \"openclaw-control-ui\",\n  \"id\": \"openclaw-control-ui\"\n}\n```\n\n[Thu 2026-03-12 08:29 GMT+8] accountId在哪里维护"}],"timestamp":1773275375868}}
{"type":"message","id":"81877ba0","parentId":"9bef7d9a","timestamp":"2026-03-12T00:29:41.516Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"用户问的是 accountId 在哪里维护。这是关于 OpenClaw 配置的问题。accountId 通常是在配置文件中定义的，用于标识不同的账号实例（比如多个 WhatsApp 账号、多个 Telegram bot 等）。\n\n我需要告诉用户 accountId 的维护位置。根据 OpenClaw 的架构，这通常在：\n1. 配置文件（config.json 或类似）\n2. 或者在连接/渠道配置中\n\n让我给出准确的回答。","thinkingSignature":"reasoning_content"},{"type":"text","text":"`accountId` 在 **OpenClaw 的配置文件** 中维护，具体位置取决于你使用的渠道：\n\n**常见位置：**\n\n| 渠道 | 配置位置 |\n|------|----------|\n| **WhatsApp** | `config.json` → `whatsapp.accounts[]` |\n| **Telegram** | `config.json` → `telegram.bots[]` |\n| **Discord** | `config.json` → `discord.servers[]` |\n| **Signal** | `config.json` → `signal.accounts[]` |\n\n**示例（WhatsApp）：**\n\n```json\n{\n  \"whatsapp\": {\n    \"accounts\": [\n      {\n        \"accountId\": \"personal\",\n        \"name\": \"我的个人号\",\n        \"phone\": \"+86123456789\"\n      },\n      {\n        \"accountId\": \"work\",\n        \"name\": \"工作号\",\n        \"phone\": \"+86987654321\"\n      }\n    ]\n  }\n}\n```\n\n**关键点：**\n\n- `accountId` 是你自定义的标识符（如 `\"personal\"`, `\"work\"`, `\"bot1\"`）\n- 在 `bindings` 中引用这个 ID 来路由消息\n- 配置文件通常在 OpenClaw 安装目录或用户配置目录\n\n想查看具体配置，可以运行 `openclaw status` 或检查配置文件位置。"}],"api":"openai-completions","provider":"dashscope-coding","model":"qwen3.5-plus","usage":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":0,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"stop","timestamp":1773275375872}}
{"type":"message","id":"4c3e639e","parentId":"81877ba0","timestamp":"2026-03-12T00:30:14.079Z","message":{"role":"user","content":[{"type":"text","text":"Sender (untrusted metadata):\n```json\n{\n  \"label\": \"openclaw-control-ui\",\n  \"id\": \"openclaw-control-ui\"\n}\n```\n\n[Thu 2026-03-12 08:30 GMT+8] \"session\": {\n \"dmScope\": \"per-channel-peer\",\n \"identityLinks\": {\n // \"alice\": [\"telegram:123456789\", \"discord:987654321012345678\"]\n },\n \"reset\": {\n \"mode\": \"daily\",\n \"atHour\": 4,\n \"idleMinutes\": 120\n },\n \"resetByType\": {\n \"thread\": { \"mode\": \"daily\", \"atHour\": 4 },\n \"direct\": { \"mode\": \"idle\", \"idleMinutes\": 240 },\n \"group\": { \"mode\": \"idle\", \"idleMinutes\": 120 }\n },\n \"resetTriggers\": [\"/new\", \"/reset\"],\n \"store\": \"~/.openclaw/agents/{agentId}/sessions/sessions.json\",\n \"parentForkMaxTokens\": 100000,\n \"maintenance\": {\n \"mode\": \"warn\",\n \"pruneAfter\": \"30d\",\n \"maxEntries\": 500,\n \"rotateBytes\": \"10mb\",\n \"resetArchiveRetention\": \"30d\",\n \"maxDiskBytes\": \"500mb\",\n \"highWaterBytes\": \"400mb\"\n },\n \"threadBindings\": {\n \"enabled\": true,\n \"idleHours\": 24,\n \"maxAgeHours\": 0\n },\n \"mainKey\": \"main\",\n \"agentToAgent\": {\n \"maxPingPongTurns\": 5\n },\n \"sendPolicy\": {\n \"rules\": [\n // {\n // \"action\": \"deny\",\n // \"match\": { \"channel\": \"discord\", \"chatType\": \"group\" }\n // }\n ]\n },\n \"typingMode\": \"instant\",\n \"typingIntervalSeconds\": 6\n },\n详细说一下这个配置"}],"timestamp":1773275414074}}
{"type":"message","id":"52f2de45","parentId":"4c3e639e","timestamp":"2026-03-12T00:30:28.588Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"用户想了解 OpenClaw 的 session 配置，我需要详细解释每个配置项的作用。这是关于会话管理的核心配置，包括会话作用域、身份链接、重置策略、存储、维护、线程绑定、agent 间通信、发送策略等。\n","thinkingSignature":"reasoning_content"},{"type":"text","text":"这是 **OpenClaw 会话（Session）管理配置**，控制如何存储、重置、维护用户会话。\n\n---\n\n## 核心配置详解\n\n### 📍 会话作用域\n```json\n\"dmScope\": \"per-channel-peer\"\n```\n- **作用**：定义私聊会话的区分粒度\n- **值**：`per-channel-peer` = 每个渠道 + 每个用户 = 独立会话\n- 例：同一个人在 Telegram 和 WhatsApp 会有两个独立会话\n\n---\n\n### 🔗 身份链接\n```json\n\"identityLinks\": {\n  // \"alice\": [\"telegram:123456789\", \"discord:987654321012345678\"]\n}\n```\n- **作用**：把不同渠道的同一个用户关联起来\n- 启用后：Alice 在 Telegram 和 Discord 的消息共享同一会话历史\n- 目前注释掉 = 未启用\n\n---\n\n### 🔄 会话重置策略\n\n**全局重置：**\n```json\n\"reset\": {\n  \"mode\": \"daily\",        // 每天重置\n  \"atHour\": 4,           // 凌晨 4 点\n  \"idleMinutes\": 120     // 或空闲 120 分钟后重置\n}\n```\n\n**按会话类型重置：**\n```json\n\"resetByType\": {\n  \"thread\": { \"mode\": \"daily\", \"atHour\": 4 },    // 线程：每天 4 点\n  \"direct\": { \"mode\": \"idle\", \"idleMinutes\": 240 }, // 私聊：空闲 4 小时\n  \"group\": { \"mode\": \"idle\", \"idleMinutes\": 120 }   // 群聊：空闲 2 小时\n}\n```\n\n**触发命令：**\n```json\n\"resetTriggers\": [\"/new\", \"/reset\"]\n```\n- 用户发送 `/new` 或 `/reset` 手动重置会话\n\n---\n\n### 💾 存储位置\n```json\n\"store\": \"~/.openclaw/agents/{agentId}/sessions/sessions.json\"\n```\n- 会话数据存于此路径\n- `{agentId}` 自动替换为实际 agent ID\n\n---\n\n### 🧹 维护策略\n```json\n\"maintenance\": {\n  \"mode\": \"warn\",              // 超限时警告（而非拒绝）\n  \"pruneAfter\": \"30d\",         // 30 天无活动会话删除\n  \"maxEntries\": 500,           // 最多 500 条会话记录\n  \"rotateBytes\": \"10mb\",       // 单会话超 10MB 轮转\n  \"resetArchiveRetention\": \"30d\", // 重置历史保留 30 天\n  \"maxDiskBytes\": \"500mb\",     // 总会话数据上限 500MB\n  \"highWaterBytes\": \"400mb\"    // 达 400MB 开始清理\n}\n```\n\n---\n\n### 🧵 线程绑定\n```json\n\"threadBindings\": {\n  \"enabled\": true,\n  \"idleHours\": 24,    // 线程空闲 24 小时后解绑\n  \"maxAgeHours\": 0    // 0 = 无最大年龄限制\n}\n```\n- 用于 Discord 等支持线程的平台\n- 线程内对话保持上下文，超时后解绑\n\n---\n\n### 🤖 Agent 间通信\n```json\n\"agentToAgent\": {\n  \"maxPingPongTurns\": 5\n}\n```\n- 防止两个 agent 无限互相回复\n- 最多 5 轮对话后停止\n\n---\n\n### 📤 发送策略\n```json\n\"sendPolicy\": {\n  \"rules\": [\n    // {\n    //   \"action\": \"deny\",\n    //   \"match\": { \"channel\": \"discord\", \"chatType\": \"group\" }\n    // }\n  ]\n}\n```\n- 控制 agent 能否向特定渠道/聊天类型发送消息\n- 例：禁止 agent 在 Discord 群聊发言（目前注释掉）\n\n---\n\n### ⌨️ 打字指示\n```json\n\"typingMode\": \"instant\",\n\"typingIntervalSeconds\": 6\n```\n- `instant` = 立即显示打字状态\n- `6 秒` = 打字状态刷新间隔\n\n---\n\n## 总结\n\n| 模块 | 作用 |\n|------|------|\n| `dmScope` | 会话区分粒度 |\n| `identityLinks` | 跨渠道用户关联 |\n| `reset` / `resetByType` | 自动/手动重置规则 |\n| `store` | 会话存储路径 |\n| `maintenance` | 清理/归档策略 |\n| `threadBindings` | 线程会话绑定 |\n| `agentToAgent` | 防无限互聊 |\n| `sendPolicy` | 发送权限控制 |\n| `typingMode` | 打字状态显示 |\n\n需要调整任何配置可以告诉我。"}],"api":"openai-completions","provider":"dashscope-coding","model":"qwen3.5-plus","usage":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":0,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"stop","timestamp":1773275414078}}
