{"type":"message","id":"1a0489d6","parentId":"58f5b3c1","timestamp":"2026-03-12T14:50:46.164Z","message":{"role":"toolResult","toolCallId":"call_790d88f179054b669c52ca1b","toolName":"exec","content":[{"type":"text","text":"anthropic.md\r\nbedrock.md\r\nclaude-max-api-proxy.md\r\ncloudflare-ai-gateway.md\r\ndeepgram.md\r\ngithub-copilot.md\r\nglm.md\r\nhuggingface.md\r\nindex.md\r\nkilocode.md\r\nlitellm.md\r\nminimax.md\r\nmistral.md\r\nmodels.md\r\nmoonshot.md\r\nnvidia.md\r\nollama.md\r\nopenai.md\r\nopencode.md\r\nopenrouter.md\r\nqianfan.md\r\nqwen.md\r\nsynthetic.md\r\ntogether.md\r\nvenice.md\r\nvercel-ai-gateway.md\r\nvllm.md\r\nxiaomi.md\r\nzai.md"}],"details":{"status":"completed","exitCode":0,"durationMs":359,"aggregated":"anthropic.md\r\nbedrock.md\r\nclaude-max-api-proxy.md\r\ncloudflare-ai-gateway.md\r\ndeepgram.md\r\ngithub-copilot.md\r\nglm.md\r\nhuggingface.md\r\nindex.md\r\nkilocode.md\r\nlitellm.md\r\nminimax.md\r\nmistral.md\r\nmodels.md\r\nmoonshot.md\r\nnvidia.md\r\nollama.md\r\nopenai.md\r\nopencode.md\r\nopenrouter.md\r\nqianfan.md\r\nqwen.md\r\nsynthetic.md\r\ntogether.md\r\nvenice.md\r\nvercel-ai-gateway.md\r\nvllm.md\r\nxiaomi.md\r\nzai.md","cwd":"C:\\Users\\28964\\.openclaw\\workspace"},"isError":false,"timestamp":1773327046159}}
{"type":"message","id":"e98355c8","parentId":"1a0489d6","timestamp":"2026-03-12T14:50:49.407Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"看到了 qwen.md 和 qianfan.md，让我查看 qwen.md 看看是否支持 TTS。","thinkingSignature":"reasoning_content"},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_1d190ae891bb42af97209d7f","name":"read","arguments":{"path":"F:\\Program\\nvm\\node_global\\node_modules\\openclaw\\docs\\providers\\qwen.md"}}],"api":"openai-completions","provider":"dashscope-coding","model":"qwen3.5-plus","usage":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":0,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"toolUse","timestamp":1773327046164}}
{"type":"message","id":"cf775d1a","parentId":"e98355c8","timestamp":"2026-03-12T14:50:49.425Z","message":{"role":"toolResult","toolCallId":"call_1d190ae891bb42af97209d7f","toolName":"read","content":[{"type":"text","text":"---\nsummary: \"Use Qwen OAuth (free tier) in OpenClaw\"\nread_when:\n  - You want to use Qwen with OpenClaw\n  - You want free-tier OAuth access to Qwen Coder\ntitle: \"Qwen\"\n---\n\n# Qwen\n\nQwen provides a free-tier OAuth flow for Qwen Coder and Qwen Vision models\n(2,000 requests/day, subject to Qwen rate limits).\n\n## Enable the plugin\n\n```bash\nopenclaw plugins enable qwen-portal-auth\n```\n\nRestart the Gateway after enabling.\n\n## Authenticate\n\n```bash\nopenclaw models auth login --provider qwen-portal --set-default\n```\n\nThis runs the Qwen device-code OAuth flow and writes a provider entry to your\n`models.json` (plus a `qwen` alias for quick switching).\n\n## Model IDs\n\n- `qwen-portal/coder-model`\n- `qwen-portal/vision-model`\n\nSwitch models with:\n\n```bash\nopenclaw models set qwen-portal/coder-model\n```\n\n## Reuse Qwen Code CLI login\n\nIf you already logged in with the Qwen Code CLI, OpenClaw will sync credentials\nfrom `~/.qwen/oauth_creds.json` when it loads the auth store. You still need a\n`models.providers.qwen-portal` entry (use the login command above to create one).\n\n## Notes\n\n- Tokens auto-refresh; re-run the login command if refresh fails or access is revoked.\n- Default base URL: `https://portal.qwen.ai/v1` (override with\n  `models.providers.qwen-portal.baseUrl` if Qwen provides a different endpoint).\n- See [Model providers](/concepts/model-providers) for provider-wide rules.\n"}],"isError":false,"timestamp":1773327049419}}
