{"type":"message","id":"30e6b907","parentId":"c1ab5afc","timestamp":"2026-03-12T16:04:32.108Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"我刚才写了一个带示例 Token 的脚本文件，现在需要生成一个真正的随机 Token 并更新脚本，然后告诉用户如何执行。","thinkingSignature":"reasoning_content"},{"type":"text","text":"我已经创建了一个 PowerShell 脚本文件。现在我帮你生成一个真正的随机 Token 并更新脚本：\n\n**请在 PowerShell 中执行以下命令：**\n\n```powershell\n# 1. 生成随机 Token 并设置环境变量\n$token = -join ((65..90) + (97..122) + (48..57) | Get-Random -Count 64 | ForEach-Object {[char]$_})\n[System.Environment]::SetEnvironmentVariable(\"WEBHOOK_TOKEN\", $token, \"User\")\n\n# 2. 验证设置\necho $env:WEBHOOK_TOKEN\n\n# 3. 重启 Gateway\nopenclaw gateway restart\n```\n\n---\n\n## 📋 或者手动执行（分步）\n\n### 步骤 1：生成 Token\n```powershell\n-join ((65..90) + (97..122) + (48..57) | Get-Random -Count 64 | ForEach-Object {[char]$_})\n```\n**记下输出的 64 位随机字符串**\n\n### 步骤 2：设置环境变量\n```powershell\n[System.Environment]::SetEnvironmentVariable(\n  \"WEBHOOK_TOKEN\",\n  \"上面生成的字符串\",\n  \"User\"\n)\n```\n\n### 步骤 3：验证\n```powershell\necho $env:WEBHOOK_TOKEN\n```\n\n### 步骤 4：重启 Gateway\n```powershell\nopenclaw gateway restart\n```\n\n---\n\n## ✅ 完成后\n\n错误 `[SECRETS_RELOADER_DEGRADED]` 应该消失，Cron 功能正常工作。\n\n需要我帮你执行重启吗？"}],"api":"openai-completions","provider":"dashscope-coding","model":"qwen3.5-plus","usage":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":0,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"stop","timestamp":1773331465347}}
