{"type":"message","id":"c40d1189","parentId":"0c931eec","timestamp":"2026-03-12T16:18:30.339Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"用户让我帮忙安装可靠的插件。但我之前尝试用子 agent 执行命令失败了，因为子 agent 在沙盒中无法访问宿主机的环境变量。\n\n我需要用 process 工具直接执行命令来安装插件。让我先检查是否有可用的会话，然后执行安装命令。\n\n可靠的插件推荐：\n1. @openclaw/github - GitHub 集成（开发者必备）\n2. @openclaw/notion - Notion 集成\n3. @openclaw/openprose - 文字润色\n4. @openclaw/web-scraper - 网页抓取\n\n但我不确定用户具体需要什么插件，我应该先问用户需求，或者安装几个通用的可靠插件。\n\n让我尝试用 process 执行安装命令。\n","thinkingSignature":"reasoning_content"},{"type":"text","text":"好的，我来帮你安装几个可靠且实用的官方插件。\n\n"},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_a1de5f0575804901adbe11c9","name":"process","arguments":{"action":"exec","data":"openclaw plugins install @openclaw/github","eof":true}}],"api":"openai-completions","provider":"dashscope-coding","model":"qwen3.5-plus","usage":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":0,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"toolUse","timestamp":1773332305418}}
