{"type":"message","id":"fb82ef8e","parentId":"318040a5","timestamp":"2026-03-12T16:24:28.622Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"配置已更新完成，子 agent 正在尝试重启 Gateway，我需要总结已启用的插件并告知用户等待重启结果或提供手动重启的替代方案。\n","thinkingSignature":"reasoning_content"},{"type":"text","text":"已派子 agent 重启 Gateway。\n\n---\n\n## ✅ 配置更新完成\n\n**已启用的插件：**\n\n| 插件 | 状态 | 用途 |\n|------|------|------|\n| `qwen-portal-auth` | ✅ 启用 | 通义千问认证 |\n| `@openclaw/github` | ✅ 新增 | GitHub 事件通知 |\n| `@openclaw/openprose` | ✅ 新增 | 文字润色改写 |\n| `@openclaw/web-scraper` | ✅ 新增 | 网页数据抓取 |\n\n---\n\n## 📋 插件使用命令\n\n### GitHub 插件\n```\n/github status          # 查看 GitHub 状态\n/github connect         # 连接 GitHub 账号\n```\n\n### 文字润色插件\n```\n/prose 把这段话改得更正式：xxx\n/prose 翻译成英文：xxx\n/prose 简化这段话：xxx\n```\n\n### 网页抓取插件\n```\n/scrape https://example.com 提取所有标题\n/scrape https://example.com 获取正文内容\n```\n\n---\n\n**等 Gateway 重启完成后，插件就可以使用了！** 如果重启失败，请手动执行：\n\n```powershell\nopenclaw gateway restart\n```"}],"api":"openai-completions","provider":"dashscope-coding","model":"qwen3.5-plus","usage":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":0,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"stop","timestamp":1773332662214}}
