{"type":"message","id":"ca275233","parentId":"0360ea95","timestamp":"2026-03-12T16:37:02.854Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"搜索 memory 没有找到 logging 配置的信息。让我用 grep 或 read 来查找配置文件中是否有 logging 相关的配置定义。","thinkingSignature":"reasoning_content"},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_fa65ccda28ea4043b8adec3f","name":"read","arguments":{"path":"F:\\Program\\nvm\\node_global\\node_modules\\openclaw\\docs\\gateway\\configuration-reference.md","limit":200,"offset":2700}}],"api":"openai-completions","provider":"dashscope-coding","model":"qwen3.5-plus","usage":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":0,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"toolUse","timestamp":1773333411788}}
{"type":"message","id":"fbf0557f","parentId":"ca275233","timestamp":"2026-03-12T16:37:02.875Z","message":{"role":"toolResult","toolCallId":"call_fa65ccda28ea4043b8adec3f","toolName":"read","content":[{"type":"text","text":"\n### `SecretRef`\n\nUse one object shape:\n\n```json5\n{ source: \"env\" | \"file\" | \"exec\", provider: \"default\", id: \"...\" }\n```\n\nValidation:\n\n- `provider` pattern: `^[a-z][a-z0-9_-]{0,63}$`\n- `source: \"env\"` id pattern: `^[A-Z][A-Z0-9_]{0,127}$`\n- `source: \"file\"` id: absolute JSON pointer (for example `\"/providers/openai/apiKey\"`)\n- `source: \"exec\"` id pattern: `^[A-Za-z0-9][A-Za-z0-9._:/-]{0,255}$`\n\n### Supported credential surface\n\n- Canonical matrix: [SecretRef Credential Surface](/reference/secretref-credential-surface)\n- `secrets apply` targets supported `openclaw.json` credential paths.\n- `auth-profiles.json` refs are included in runtime resolution and audit coverage.\n\n### Secret providers config\n\n```json5\n{\n  secrets: {\n    providers: {\n      default: { source: \"env\" }, // optional explicit env provider\n      filemain: {\n        source: \"file\",\n        path: \"~/.openclaw/secrets.json\",\n        mode: \"json\",\n        timeoutMs: 5000,\n      },\n      vault: {\n        source: \"exec\",\n        command: \"/usr/local/bin/openclaw-vault-resolver\",\n        passEnv: [\"PATH\", \"VAULT_ADDR\"],\n      },\n    },\n    defaults: {\n      env: \"default\",\n      file: \"filemain\",\n      exec: \"vault\",\n    },\n  },\n}\n```\n\nNotes:\n\n- `file` provider supports `mode: \"json\"` and `mode: \"singleValue\"` (`id` must be `\"value\"` in singleValue mode).\n- `exec` provider requires an absolute `command` path and uses protocol payloads on stdin/stdout.\n- By default, symlink command paths are rejected. Set `allowSymlinkCommand: true` to allow symlink paths while validating the resolved target path.\n- If `trustedDirs` is configured, the trusted-dir check applies to the resolved target path.\n- `exec` child environment is minimal by default; pass required variables explicitly with `passEnv`.\n- Secret refs are resolved at activation time into an in-memory snapshot, then request paths read the snapshot only.\n- Active-surface filtering applies during activation: unresolved refs on enabled surfaces fail startup/reload, while inactive surfaces are skipped with diagnostics.\n\n---\n\n## Auth storage\n\n```json5\n{\n  auth: {\n    profiles: {\n      \"anthropic:me@example.com\": { provider: \"anthropic\", mode: \"oauth\", email: \"me@example.com\" },\n      \"anthropic:work\": { provider: \"anthropic\", mode: \"api_key\" },\n    },\n    order: {\n      anthropic: [\"anthropic:me@example.com\", \"anthropic:work\"],\n    },\n  },\n}\n```\n\n- Per-agent profiles are stored at `<agentDir>/auth-profiles.json`.\n- `auth-profiles.json` supports value-level refs (`keyRef` for `api_key`, `tokenRef` for `token`).\n- Static runtime credentials come from in-memory resolved snapshots; legacy static `auth.json` entries are scrubbed when discovered.\n- Legacy OAuth imports from `~/.openclaw/credentials/oauth.json`.\n- See [OAuth](/concepts/oauth).\n- Secrets runtime behavior and `audit/configure/apply` tooling: [Secrets Management](/gateway/secrets).\n\n---\n\n## Logging\n\n```json5\n{\n  logging: {\n    level: \"info\",\n    file: \"/tmp/openclaw/openclaw.log\",\n    consoleLevel: \"info\",\n    consoleStyle: \"pretty\", // pretty | compact | json\n    redactSensitive: \"tools\", // off | tools\n    redactPatterns: [\"\\\\bTOKEN\\\\b\\\\s*[=:]\\\\s*([\\\"']?)([^\\\\s\\\"']+)\\\\1\"],\n  },\n}\n```\n\n- Default log file: `/tmp/openclaw/openclaw-YYYY-MM-DD.log`.\n- Set `logging.file` for a stable path.\n- `consoleLevel` bumps to `debug` when `--verbose`.\n\n---\n\n## CLI\n\n```json5\n{\n  cli: {\n    banner: {\n      taglineMode: \"off\", // random | default | off\n    },\n  },\n}\n```\n\n- `cli.banner.taglineMode` controls banner tagline style:\n  - `\"random\"` (default): rotating funny/seasonal taglines.\n  - `\"default\"`: fixed neutral tagline (`All your chats, one OpenClaw.`).\n  - `\"off\"`: no tagline text (banner title/version still shown).\n- To hide the entire banner (not just taglines), set env `OPENCLAW_HIDE_BANNER=1`.\n\n---\n\n## Wizard\n\nMetadata written by CLI wizards (`onboard`, `configure`, `doctor`):\n\n```json5\n{\n  wizard: {\n    lastRunAt: \"2026-01-01T00:00:00.000Z\",\n    lastRunVersion: \"2026.1.4\",\n    lastRunCommit: \"abc1234\",\n    lastRunCommand: \"configure\",\n    lastRunMode: \"local\",\n  },\n}\n```\n\n---\n\n## Identity\n\n```json5\n{\n  agents: {\n    list: [\n      {\n        id: \"main\",\n        identity: {\n          name: \"Samantha\",\n          theme: \"helpful sloth\",\n          emoji: \"🦥\",\n          avatar: \"avatars/samantha.png\",\n        },\n      },\n    ],\n  },\n}\n```\n\nWritten by the macOS onboarding assistant. Derives defaults:\n\n- `messages.ackReaction` from `identity.emoji` (falls back to 👀)\n- `mentionPatterns` from `identity.name`/`identity.emoji`\n- `avatar` accepts: workspace-relative path, `http(s)` URL, or `data:` URI\n\n---\n\n## Bridge (legacy, removed)\n\nCurrent builds no longer include the TCP bridge. Nodes connect over the Gateway WebSocket. `bridge.*` keys are no longer part of the config schema (validation fails until removed; `openclaw doctor --fix` can strip unknown keys).\n\n<Accordion title=\"Legacy bridge config (historical reference)\">\n\n```json\n{\n  \"bridge\": {\n    \"enabled\": true,\n    \"port\": 18790,\n    \"bind\": \"tailnet\",\n    \"tls\": {\n      \"enabled\": true,\n      \"autoGenerate\": true\n    }\n  }\n}\n```\n\n</Accordion>\n\n---\n\n## Cron\n\n\n[83 more lines in file. Use offset=2900 to continue.]"}],"isError":false,"timestamp":1773333422865}}
{"type":"message","id":"aab9b8b5","parentId":"fbf0557f","timestamp":"2026-03-12T16:37:15.194Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"找到了！文档中有 Logging 配置的正确格式。用户的配置与官方文档对比有几个字段不正确：\n\n1. `format` 应该是 `consoleStyle`\n2. 缺少 `consoleLevel` 字段\n3. `rotation` 配置在官方文档中没有提到，可能不支持\n\n让我告诉用户正确的配置格式。","thinkingSignature":"reasoning_content"},{"type":"text","text":"找到问题了！**OpenClaw 的 `logging` 配置字段名称和你写的不一样！**\n\n---\n\n## ❌ 你的配置（错误）\n\n```json\n\"logging\": {\n  \"level\": \"info\",\n  \"format\": \"json\",          // ❌ 应该是 consoleStyle\n  \"file\": \"~/.openclaw/logs/openclaw.log\",\n  \"console\": true,           // ❌ 没有这个字段\n  \"rotation\": {              // ❌ 不支持这个配置\n    \"maxSize\": \"10mb\",\n    \"maxFiles\": 5\n  }\n}\n```\n\n---\n\n## ✅ 正确配置（根据官方文档）\n\n```json\n\"logging\": {\n  \"level\": \"info\",\n  \"file\": \"/tmp/openclaw/openclaw.log\",\n  \"consoleLevel\": \"info\",\n  \"consoleStyle\": \"pretty\",\n  \"redactSensitive\": \"tools\",\n  \"redactPatterns\": [\"\\\\bTOKEN\\\\b\\\\s*[=:]\\\\s*([\\\"']?)([^\\\\s\\\"']+)\\\\1\"]\n}\n```\n\n---\n\n## 📋 正确字段说明\n\n| 字段 | 作用 | 可选值 |\n|------|------|--------|\n| `level` | 日志文件级别 | `\"info\"`, `\"debug\"`, `\"warn\"`, `\"error\"` |\n| `file` | 日志文件路径 | 绝对路径 |\n| `consoleLevel` | 控制台日志级别 | `\"info\"`, `\"debug\"`, `\"warn\"`, `\"error\"` |\n| `consoleStyle` | 控制台输出格式 | `\"pretty\"`, `\"compact\"`, `\"json\"` |\n| `redactSensitive` | 脱敏敏感信息 | `\"off\"`, `\"tools\"` |\n| `redactPatterns` | 自定义脱敏正则 | 正则表达式数组 |\n\n---\n\n## 🔧 快速修复\n\n**删除 `logging` 配置**（使用默认设置），或者改为：\n\n```json\n\"logging\": {\n  \"level\": \"info\",\n  \"file\": \"/tmp/openclaw/openclaw.log\",\n  \"consoleLevel\": \"info\",\n  \"consoleStyle\": \"pretty\"\n}\n```\n\n---\n\n## 📝 注意事项\n\n| 注意 | 说明 |\n|------|------|\n| 默认日志路径 | `/tmp/openclaw/openclaw-YYYY-MM-DD.log` |\n| 不支持 `rotation` | 日志轮转是自动管理的 |\n| 不支持 `console` | 用 `consoleLevel` 控制 |\n| 不支持 `format` | 用 `consoleStyle` 控制 |\n\n---\n\n**总结：** 删除或修正 `logging` 配置，使用官方支持的字段名称！"}],"api":"openai-completions","provider":"dashscope-coding","model":"qwen3.5-plus","usage":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":0,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"stop","timestamp":1773333422873}}
{"type":"message","id":"4c036527","parentId":"aab9b8b5","timestamp":"2026-03-12T16:38:10.242Z","message":{"role":"user","content":[{"type":"text","text":"Sender (untrusted metadata):\n```json\n{\n  \"label\": \"openclaw-control-ui\",\n  \"id\": \"openclaw-control-ui\"\n}\n```\n\n[Fri 2026-03-13 00:38 GMT+8] \"identity\": {\n \"name\": \"Samantha\",\n \"theme\": \"helpful assistant\",\n \"emoji\": \"🦥\",\n \"avatar\": \"avatars/samantha.png\",\n \"ackReaction\": \"👀\"\n },\n这个配置的作用"}],"timestamp":1773333490230}}
{"type":"message","id":"f74849a7","parentId":"4c036527","timestamp":"2026-03-12T16:38:43.082Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"用户询问 identity 配置的作用，我需要详细解释每个字段的含义和用途。","thinkingSignature":"reasoning_content"},{"type":"text","text":"# Identity 配置详解\n\n---\n\n## 🎯 核心作用\n\n**Identity = Agent 身份定义**\n\n控制 Agent 的\"人格\"特征，包括：\n- 名字\n- 主题风格\n- 表情符号\n- 头像\n- 默认反应\n\n---\n\n## 📋 配置解读\n\n```json\n\"identity\": {\n  \"name\": \"Samantha\",\n  \"theme\": \"helpful assistant\",\n  \"emoji\": \"🦥\",\n  \"avatar\": \"avatars/samantha.png\",\n  \"ackReaction\": \"👀\"\n}\n```\n\n---\n\n## 🔍 字段详解\n\n### 1. `name` - Agent 名字\n\n```json\n\"name\": \"Samantha\"\n```\n\n| 说明 | 值 |\n|------|-----|\n| **作用** | Agent 的显示名称 |\n| **当前值** | `\"Samantha\"` |\n| **用途** | 系统提示、用户称呼、@提及匹配 |\n\n**影响范围：**\n- 系统提示中会提到 \"You are Samantha\"\n- 用户可以用 `@Samantha` 提及\n- 回复前缀可能包含名字\n\n**常用名字：**\n| 名字 | 风格 |\n|------|------|\n| `Samantha` | 温暖、友好 |\n| `Clawd` | 技术、专业 |\n| `Alice` | 经典 AI |\n| `Nova` | 现代、简洁 |\n\n---\n\n### 2. `theme` - 主题风格\n\n```json\n\"theme\": \"helpful assistant\"\n```\n\n| 说明 | 值 |\n|------|------|\n| **作用** | 定义 Agent 的性格和行为风格 |\n| **当前值** | `\"helpful assistant\"` = 乐于助人的助手 |\n| **用途** | 影响系统提示，指导 Agent 行为 |\n\n**常用主题：**\n| 主题 | 含义 |\n|------|------|\n| `\"helpful assistant\"` | 乐于助人、友好 |\n| `\"professional\"` | 专业、正式 |\n| `\"casual friend\"` | 随意、像朋友 |\n| `\"technical expert\"` | 技术专家 |\n| `\"creative writer\"` | 创意作家 |\n| `\"research analyst\"` | 研究分析师 |\n\n---\n\n### 3. `emoji` - 表情符号\n\n```json\n\"emoji\": \"🦥\"\n```\n\n| 说明 | 值 |\n|------|------|\n| **作用** | Agent 的标志性 emoji |\n| **当前值** | `🦥` = 树懒（悠闲、可靠） |\n| **用途** | 消息前缀、反应、视觉标识 |\n\n**自动应用：**\n- 如果 `messages.ackReaction` 未配置，默认使用此 emoji\n- 可能用于消息前缀\n- 在 UI 中作为 Agent 标识\n\n**常用 emoji：**\n| Emoji | 含义 |\n|-------|------|\n| `🦥` | 树懒（悠闲、可靠） |\n| `🦞` | 龙虾（独特、有趣） |\n| `🤖` | 机器人（经典 AI） |\n| `✨` | 星星（魔法、神奇） |\n| `🧠` | 大脑（智慧） |\n| `⚡` | 闪电（快速） |\n\n---\n\n### 4. `avatar` - 头像\n\n```json\n\"avatar\": \"avatars/samantha.png\"\n```\n\n| 说明 | 值 |\n|------|------|\n| **作用** | Agent 的头像图片 |\n| **当前值** | `avatars/samantha.png`（相对路径） |\n| **用途** | UI 中显示 Agent 形象 |\n\n**支持的路径类型：**\n| 类型 | 示例 | 说明 |\n|------|------|------|\n| **相对路径** | `avatars/samantha.png` | 相对于 workspace |\n| **绝对路径** | `C:/Users/xxx/avatar.png` | 完整路径 |\n| **HTTP URL** | `https://example.com/avatar.png` | 网络图片 |\n| **Data URI** | `data:image/png;base64,...` | 内嵌图片 |\n\n**头像建议：**\n- 尺寸：`256x256` 或 `512x512`\n- 格式：PNG（支持透明）\n- 风格：与 `theme` 匹配\n\n---\n\n### 5. `ackReaction` - 确认反应\n\n```json\n\"ackReaction\": \"👀\"\n```\n\n| 说明 | 值 |\n|------|------|\n| **作用** | 收到消息时自动添加的 emoji 反应 |\n| **当前值** | `👀` = 眼睛（\"我看到了\"） |\n| **用途** | 类似已读回执，表示收到消息 |\n\n**与 `messages.ackReaction` 的关系：**\n- `identity.ackReaction` = 此 Agent 的默认反应\n- `messages.ackReaction` = 全局配置（优先级更高）\n\n**常用反应：**\n| Emoji | 含义 |\n|-------|------|\n| `👀` | 看到了、关注 |\n| `👍` | 好的、同意 |\n| `❤️` | 喜欢、感谢 |\n| `✅` | 完成、确认 |\n| `🙌` | 庆祝、支持 |\n\n---\n\n## 📊 完整配置作用总结\n\n| 字段 | 你的配置 | 作用 | 评价 |\n|------|----------|------|------|\n| `name` | `\"Samantha\"` | Agent 名字 | ✅ 友好 |\n| `theme` | `\"helpful assistant\"` | 性格风格 | ✅ 合适 |\n| `emoji` | `🦥` | 标志表情 | ✅ 独特 |\n| `avatar` | `avatars/samantha.png` | 头像图片 | ✅ |\n| `ackReaction` | `👀` | 确认反应 | ✅ 合理 |\n\n---\n\n## 🎯 实际效果\n\n### 系统提示生成\n```\nYou are Samantha, a helpful assistant.\nYour signature emoji is 🦥.\n```\n\n### UI 显示\n```\n┌─────────────────────────┐\n│ 🦥 Samantha            │\n│ [头像图片]              │\n└─────────────────────────┘\n```\n\n### 消息反应\n```\n用户：你好\n  ↓\nAgent: 👀（反应）\nAgent: 🦥 你好！有什么可以帮你？（回复）\n```\n\n---\n\n## 🏠 配置位置\n\n**注意：** `identity` 配置可以在两个地方：\n\n### 1. 全局配置（已废弃）\n```json\n{\n  \"identity\": { ... }  // ❌ 旧版本\n}\n```\n\n### 2. Agent 列表配置（推荐）\n```json\n{\n  \"agents\": {\n    \"list\": [\n      {\n        \"id\": \"main\",\n        \"identity\": {\n          \"name\": \"Samantha\",\n          \"theme\": \"helpful assistant\",\n          \"emoji\": \"🦥\",\n          \"avatar\": \"avatars/samantha.png\"\n        }\n      }\n    ]\n  }\n}\n```\n\n---\n\n## 📋 完整 Agent 配置示例\n\n```json\n{\n  \"agents\": {\n    \"list\": [\n      {\n        \"id\": \"main\",\n        \"default\": true,\n        \"name\": \"Main Agent\",\n        \"workspace\": \"~/.openclaw/workspace\",\n        \"identity\": {\n          \"name\": \"Samantha\",\n          \"theme\": \"helpful assistant\",\n          \"emoji\": \"🦥\",\n          \"avatar\": \"avatars/samantha.png\",\n          \"ackReaction\": \"👀\"\n        },\n        \"groupChat\": {\n          \"mentionPatterns\": [\"@Samantha\", \"@助手\"]\n        }\n      },\n      {\n        \"id\": \"work\",\n        \"name\": \"Work Agent\",\n        \"identity\": {\n          \"name\": \"Atlas\",\n          \"theme\": \"professional assistant\",\n          \"emoji\": \"💼\",\n          \"avatar\": \"avatars/atlas.png\"\n        }\n      }\n    ]\n  }\n}\n```\n\n---\n\n## 🎨 Identity 衍生配置\n\n配置 `identity` 后，OpenClaw 会自动衍生以下配置：\n\n### 1. 自动设置 `messages.ackReaction`\n```json\n// 如果未配置 messages.ackReaction\n// 自动使用 identity.emoji\n\"messages\": {\n  \"ackReaction\": \"🦥\"  // 从 identity.emoji 继承\n}\n```\n\n### 2. 自动添加 `mentionPatterns`\n```json\n\"agents\": {\n  \"list\": [{\n    \"groupChat\": {\n      \"mentionPatterns\": [\"@Samantha\", \"@🦥\"]  // 从 name 和 emoji 衍生\n    }\n  }]\n}\n```\n\n---\n\n## ⚠️ 注意事项\n\n| 注意 | 说明 |\n|------|------|\n| 头像路径 | 确保文件存在，或使用 URL |\n| Emoji 兼容性 | 使用常见 emoji，避免显示问题 |\n| Theme 影响 | 会影响系统提示，谨慎选择 |\n| 多 Agent | 每个 Agent 可以有独立 identity |\n\n---\n\n## 🎯 推荐配置（按场景）\n\n### 个人助理\n```json\n{\n  \"identity\": {\n    \"name\": \"Samantha\",\n    \"theme\": \"helpful assistant\",\n    \"emoji\": \"🦥\",\n    \"avatar\": \"avatars/samantha.png\",\n    \"ackReaction\": \"👀\"\n  }\n}\n```\n\n### 工作助手\n```json\n{\n  \"identity\": {\n    \"name\": \"Atlas\",\n    \"theme\": \"professional assistant\",\n    \"emoji\": \"💼\",\n    \"avatar\": \"avatars/atlas.png\",\n    \"ackReaction\": \"✅\"\n  }\n}\n```\n\n### 创意伙伴\n```json\n{\n  \"identity\": {\n    \"name\": \"Muse\",\n    \"theme\": \"creative companion\",\n    \"emoji\": \"✨\",\n    \"avatar\": \"avatars/muse.png\",\n    \"ackReaction\": \"💡\"\n  }\n}\n```\n\n### 技术专家\n```json\n{\n  \"identity\": {\n    \"name\": \"Codey\",\n    \"theme\": \"technical expert\",\n    \"emoji\": \"🤖\",\n    \"avatar\": \"avatars/codey.png\",\n    \"ackReaction\": \"⚡\"\n  }\n}\n```\n\n---\n\n## 📊 配置对比\n\n| 字段 | 必需 | 默认值 | 你的配置 |\n|------|------|--------|----------|\n| `name` | ✅ | `\"Assistant\"` | `\"Samantha\"` |\n| `theme` | ❌ | `\"helpful assistant\"` | `\"helpful assistant\"` |\n| `emoji` | ❌ | `\"🤖\"` | `\"🦥\"` |\n| `avatar` | ❌ | 无 | `\"avatars/samantha.png\"` |\n| `ackReaction` | ❌ | 从 emoji 继承 | `\"👀\"` |\n\n---\n\n**总结：** 你的 Identity 配置定义了一个名叫 \"Samantha\" 的友好助手形象，使用树懒 🦥 作为标志，配置完整且合理！"}],"api":"openai-completions","provider":"dashscope-coding","model":"qwen3.5-plus","usage":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":0,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"stop","timestamp":1773333490236}}
