{"type":"message","id":"ce8af1d1","parentId":"42717e11","timestamp":"2026-03-12T16:40:11.363Z","message":{"role":"toolResult","toolCallId":"call_cf44a85c2ec84ea1a3450bef","toolName":"read","content":[{"type":"text","text":"        120000,\n        300000\n      ],\n      \"retryOn\": [\n        \"rate_limit\",\n        \"overloaded\",\n        \"network\",\n        \"server_error\"\n      ]\n    },\n    \"webhookToken\": \"p8cVPh7XgFU1GBKMOmyz0juJTxf9aqdrE4i5nvlZCbSD3LH2oW6kYAweItsNQR\",\n    \"sessionRetention\": \"24h\",\n    \"runLog\": {\n      \"maxBytes\": \"2mb\",\n      \"keepLines\": 2000\n    }\n  },\n  \"hooks\": {\n    \"internal\": {\n      \"enabled\": true,\n      \"entries\": {\n        \"bootstrap-extra-files\": {\n          \"enabled\": true\n        },\n        \"command-logger\": {\n          \"enabled\": true\n        },\n        \"session-memory\": {\n          \"enabled\": true\n        },\n        \"boot-md\": {\n          \"enabled\": true\n        }\n      }\n    }\n  },\n  \"gateway\": {\n    \"port\": 12328,\n    \"mode\": \"local\",\n    \"bind\": \"loopback\",\n    \"auth\": {\n      \"mode\": \"token\",\n      \"token\": \"7d3669d2a28f94bc8a45dbbf6aa43aa611380b3367660175\"\n    },\n    \"tailscale\": {\n      \"mode\": \"off\",\n      \"resetOnExit\": false\n    },\n    \"reload\": {\n      \"mode\": \"hybrid\",\n      \"debounceMs\": 300\n    },\n    \"tls\": {\n      \"enabled\": false\n    },\n    \"nodes\": {\n      \"denyCommands\": [\n        \"camera.snap\",\n        \"camera.clip\",\n        \"screen.record\",\n        \"contacts.add\",\n        \"calendar.add\",\n        \"reminders.add\",\n        \"sms.send\"\n      ]\n    }\n  },\n  \"plugins\": {\n    \"entries\": {\n      \"qwen-portal-auth\": {\n        \"enabled\": true\n      },\n      \"@openclaw/github\": {\n        \"enabled\": true\n      },\n      \"@openclaw/openprose\": {\n        \"enabled\": true\n      },\n      \"@openclaw/web-scraper\": {\n        \"enabled\": true\n      }\n    }\n  }\n}\n"}],"isError":false,"timestamp":1773333611355}}
{"type":"message","id":"c37c9b7e","parentId":"ce8af1d1","timestamp":"2026-03-12T16:40:16.366Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"让我用 openclaw doctor 命令来检查配置文件的验证错误，这样可以直接看到具体的问题所在。\n","thinkingSignature":"reasoning_content"},{"type":"text","text":"我发现了问题！你的配置中有 **`\"ownerDisplay\": \"raw\"`** 这个字段在 `commands` 中，这个字段可能不是有效的配置项。\n\n另外，让我检查一下 `logging.file` 路径在 Windows 上是否有效：\n\n"},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_ff581fd1faec44609826d5e4","name":"process","arguments":{"action":"exec","data":"openclaw doctor","eof":true}}],"api":"openai-completions","provider":"dashscope-coding","model":"qwen3.5-plus","usage":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":0,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"toolUse","timestamp":1773333611361}}
